      Ransomware
   =20
 =20
Ahahahahahahaha hahahahahaha hahahahaha:In October, the infamous ransomware=
 gang known as Conti released thousands of files stolen from the UK jewelry=
 store Graff.=C2=A0Now, the hackers would like the world to know that they =
regret their decision, perhaps in part because they released files belongin=
g to very powerful people. =E2=80=A6=E2=80=9CWe found that our sample data =
was not properly reviewed before being uploaded to the blog,=E2=80=9D the h=
ackers wrote in an announcement published on Thursday. =E2=80=9CConti guara=
ntees that any information pertaining to members of Saudi Arabia, UAE, and =
Qatar families will be deleted without any exposure and review.=E2=80=9D=E2=
=80=9COur Team apologizes to His Royal Highness Prince Mohammed bin Salman =
and any other members of the Royal Families whose names were mentioned in t=
he publication for any inconvenience,=E2=80=9D the hackers added.=C2=A0Imag=
ine being a big-time ransomware hacker, thinking that you=E2=80=99re pretty=
 tough, fancying yourself a master criminal, giving yourself an intimidatin=
g online alias, maybe even being able, in certain circumstances, to call do=
wn violence on your enemies, and then realizing one day that you=E2=80=99d =
accidentally hacked a guy who had a journalist=C2=A0kidnapped, tortured to =
death and then dismembered with a bone saw=C2=A0for=C2=A0criticizing him.Th=
ey are adding new compliance procedures to make sure this won=E2=80=99t hap=
pen again:The hackers also said that other than publishing the data on thei=
r site, they did not sell it or trade, and that from now on they will =E2=
=80=9Cimplement a more rigid data review process for any future operations.=
=E2=80=9DWe have  talked before about the  compliance function at ransomwar=
e firms. If you run a legal company, you have a compliance department to ma=
ke sure that you don=E2=80=99t do anything illegal, or at least, if your co=
mpany is really big, to keep the illegality within acceptable limits. If yo=
u run a=C2=A0criminal gang, you have concerns that are different in degree =
but directionally similar: Your whole business is doing illegal things, sur=
e, but you don=E2=80=99t want to do too many things that are too illegal. Y=
ou want to do crimes that make you money, but not crimes that get you shut =
down. You want to steal information from rich people and extort money from =
them. But not Mohammed bin Salman! Good lord!
