 solid; background-color: #ccc;"> New York=E2=80=99s new mayor</a>:</p><blo=
ckquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">New York Mayor-elect Eric Adams said s=
chools should teach about cryptocurrency and its technology, as he vows to =
build a crypto-friendly city when he takes office in January.=C2=A0</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CWhen I talked about blockchain and Bitcoi=
ns, young people on street stopped and asked me, =E2=80=98What is that?=E2=
=80=99=E2=80=9D Adams said on CNN=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CState of the Union=E2=
