t=E2=80=99s a challenge even for experts.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">Bitcoin means a =E2=80=9Cnew way of paying for goods and services thro=
ughout the entire globe,=E2=80=9D he said. =E2=80=9CAnd that=E2=80=99s what=
 we must do - open our schools to teach the technology and teach this new w=
ay of thinking.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"=
