ds elsewhere! =E2=80=9CCrypto is a way for people to bamboozle me with tech=
nical-sounding terms and vague rhetoric about empowerment,=C2=A0and then st=
eal my money,=E2=80=9D they will think! Correctly!</p><table class=3D"heade=
